Soting the dataframe by index: 
 -> we will use "sort_index" by pandas:
    -> in Ascending Order: 
       df.sort_index(ascending=True)
    -> in Descending Order:
       df.sort_index(descending=True)


Sorting the dataframe by Spicific Column:
 -> we will use "sort_values" by pandas:
    -> in Ascending Order:
       df.sort_values(ascending = True)
    -> in Descending Order:
       df.sort_values(descending = True)
